@EagleBankAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..zyPCOrY-xXN6P7jAo3h2NEHca_XHZEfNWkMI7iaUBhA

### Health Check
GET {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 1. Create User
POST {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "phoneNumber": "07700900123",
  "address": {
    "addressLine1": "123 High Street",
    "addressLine2": "Flat 2",
    "addressLine3": "",
    "town": "London",
    "county": "Greater London",
    "postcode": "SW1A 1AA"
  }
}

###

### 2. Login (Get JWT Token)
# @name login
POST {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

###

### 3. Get User Details (Requires Auth)
GET {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/users/usr-d0813e1f7d6a4d70960781210eacdf0e
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Update User
PATCH {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/users/usr-d0813e1f7d6a4d70960781210eacdf0e
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "07700900456",
  "address": {
    "addressLine1": "456 New Street",
    "addressLine2": "",
    "addressLine3": "",
    "town": "Manchester",
    "county": "Greater Manchester",
    "postcode": "M1 1AA"
  }
}

###

### 5. Create Bank Account
POST {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Business Account",
  "accountType": "business"
}

###

### 6. Get All Accounts
GET {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Get Specific Account
GET {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/accounts/01555167
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Update Account
PATCH {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/accounts/01555167
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Account"
}

###

### 9. Create Transaction - Deposit
POST {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/accounts/01555167/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "GBP",
  "type": "deposit",
  "reference": "Initial deposit"
}

###

### 10. Create Transaction - Withdrawal
POST {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/accounts/01555167/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.00,
  "currency": "GBP",
  "type": "withdrawal",
  "reference": "ATM withdrawal"
}

###

### 11. Get All Transactions for Account
GET {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/accounts/01555167/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 12. Delete Account
DELETE {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/accounts/01648466
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 13. Delete User
DELETE {{EagleBankAPI_HostAddress}}/v1/users/usr-d0813e1f7d6a4d70960781210eacdf0e
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
